{"ts": "2026-06-07T23:27:09.541578+00:00", "update": {"model": {"messages": [{"type": "ai", "data": {"content": "Here are the setup and day-to-day development commands for the **vue3-vite-starter-template** repository:\n\n---\n\n## Install / Setup\n\n```bash\npnpm install\n```\n- The project uses **pnpm** (v10.20.0) as its package manager.  \n- Node.js version **v24** is required (see `.nvmrc`).  \n- A `preinstall` script enforces that only pnpm is used.\n\n## Dev Server (hot-reload)\n\n```bash\npnpm run dev\n```\nStarts the Vite development server with hot module replacement.\n\n## Production Build\n\n```bash\npnpm run build\n```\nCompiles and minifies the Vue app via Vite.\n\n## Preview Production Build\n\n```bash\npnpm run preview\n```\nLocally serves the built output from `dist/`.\n\n## Unit Tests\n\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit\n```\nRuns unit tests with **Vitest** (configured with `jsdom` environment, global setup, and test-utils).\n\n## Unit Tests with Coverage\n\n```bash\npnpm run test:unit-coverage\n```\nRuns Vitest in `run` mode and outputs text + JSON coverage reports.\n\n## Lint\n\n```bash\npnpm run lint\n```\nRuns **ESLint** on all `.vue`, `.ts`, `.js` files.\n\n## Lint & Auto-fix\n\n```bash\npnpm run lint-fix\n```\nRuns ESLint with the `--fix` flag to automatically correct fixable issues.\n\n---\n\n**Summary table:**\n\n| Task             | Command                  |\n|------------------|--------------------------|\n| Install          | `pnpm install`           |\n| Dev server       | `pnpm run dev`           |\n| Build            | `pnpm run build`         |\n| Preview build    | `pnpm run preview`       |\n| Unit tests       | `pnpm run test:unit`     |\n| Unit tests + cov | `pnpm run test:unit-coverage` |\n| Lint             | `pnpm run lint`          |\n| Lint & fix       | `pnpm run lint-fix`      |\n\nAll scripts are defined in the `package.json` `\"scripts\"` section and use the project's local tools (Vite, Vitest, ESLint) without global installations.", "additional_kwargs": {"refusal": null}, "response_metadata": {"token_usage": {"completion_tokens": 802, "prompt_tokens": 5134, "total_tokens": 5936, "completion_tokens_details": {"accepted_prediction_tokens": null, "audio_tokens": null, "reasoning_tokens": 313, "rejected_prediction_tokens": null}, "prompt_tokens_details": {"audio_tokens": null, "cached_tokens": 4992}, "prompt_cache_hit_tokens": 4992, "prompt_cache_miss_tokens": 142}, "model_provider": "openai", "model_name": "deepseek-v4-flash", "system_fingerprint": "fp_8b330d02d0_prod0820_fp8_kvcache_20260402", "id": "e6e14242-d085-4e48-80a6-555d2e3f85bf", "finish_reason": "stop", "logprobs": null}, "type": "ai", "name": null, "id": "lc_run--019ea469-45f7-7522-aa90-47e6ae8c9037-0", "tool_calls": [], "invalid_tool_calls": [], "usage_metadata": {"input_tokens": 5134, "output_tokens": 802, "total_tokens": 5936, "input_token_details": {"cache_read": 4992}, "output_token_details": {"reasoning": 313}}}}]}}}
